{"arkId":"cl010440678","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010440678","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Mosa\u00efque encadr\u00e9e : portrait de Louis XVIII","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Mosa\u00efque encadr\u00e9e : portrait de Louis XVIII"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Restauration (1814-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1814 - 1824","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 559 - Louis XVIII","room":"Salle 559, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1814,"endYear":1824,"imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Belloni, Francesco","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1772","place":"Rome","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1863","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q51710273"},{"label":"G\u00e9rard, Fran\u00e7ois","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1837","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1770","place":"Rome","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q163543"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2019.3.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"OA 12937","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u0027entr\u00e9e"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mosa\u00efque","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le roi Louis XVIII, repr\u00e9sent\u00e9 en buste de trois-quarts vers la droite, est v\u00eatu d\u0027une redingote bleue \u00e0 \u00e9paulettes d\u0027or